'''Covepi'starn''' was a city on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. 

It was located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] western continent, situated between the [[capital/Legends|capital]] of [[Drev'starn]] (to the northwest) and [[Navshe'starn]] (to the southeast).

